Maybe a group version of the Bard Fade that causes in place evac.  I would like to see the mob pushed back to his bind though.  For this kind of thing I would say I don't want it to be immediately reusable for exploit reasons, but I think it could be a Very useful item.  Bard fade is controlled by consuming decent mana and having absolute crap for mana regen.  Wizards should have something similar.  I don't know what would be the best idea to control this other than maybe Endurance, but we need to find a way that a lack of endurance is a detriment to us other than just this spell.  Maybe tie the Harvests into Endurance so we have to balance Aggro with the ability to save the group?<br />
<br />
Not sure, but I also say I like the ideas above.</div>
